^^^ 1. Fill in your profile

Click where it says "your profile" just above this box and fill in the form. Don't forget a picture. We want to see your lovely face!

^^^ 2. Tag yourself

Tags help colleagues identify your expertise, interests, and hobbies. On your profile page, type a descriptive tag into the "Tags" box then click "Add Tag".

^^^ 3. Post a Signal

Tell colleagues what you're doing, ask a question, post a document, picture, or link. Just type your message in the Activities box, and click "Post".

^^^ 4. Join a group...or start your own

Groups help you discuss and collaborate with specific communities or interest groups. To see a list of available groups, click on "Group Directory" under the Groups header in the gray bar at the top of this screen.
